189
00:08:36,340 --> 00:08:38,800
"I don't remember being told to be so generous."

190
00:08:39,980 --> 00:08:44,580
"I'm sorry to say this, but we are police officers."

191
00:08:45,060 --> 00:08:46,640
"Please help us."

192
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,760
"I'm glad you said that."

193
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:50,520
"Right, everyone?"

194
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:51,500
"Yes."

195
00:08:51,920 --> 00:08:53,900
