202
00:09:11,620 --> 00:09:16,220
"Please leave this case to the great detective, Sherlock Ryozu."

203
00:09:17,760 --> 00:09:20,840
"I can't help it. I'll leave it to you for a while."

204
00:09:23,580 --> 00:09:26,960
"The crime took place within ten seconds of the power outage."

205
00:09:27,860 --> 00:09:31,360
"The culprit stole a diamond from the bag of Lady Christie's wife."

206
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:34,720
"At that time, he dropped the bag on the floor in a hurry."

207
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:37,320
"Therefore, the police officer who was not there at the time of the power outage,"

208
00:09:37,860 --> 00:09:42,900
"and the waitress, Miss Terry, and the driver, Mr. Akagawa Kyotaro, may be exempted."

209
00:09:43,540 --> 00:09:46,240
"Of course, the victim, Lady Christie, too."

210
00:09:47,540 --> 00:09:52,120
"And we, the police officers, will be the four guests."

211
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:56,220
"So I thought about it."

212
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:59,820
"And I found a person who had a great motive in this."

213
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,000
"That is..."

214
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:03,820
"You!"

215
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:05,080
"Mr. Elari!"

216
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:09,100
"Are you stupid? Why did I..."

217
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:13,440
"The Nakagawa Railway and Seikyū Railway, which you are the president of,"

218
00:10:13,620 --> 00:10:15,040
"were rival companies."

219
00:10:16,280 --> 00:10:19,920
"If the media finds out that the diamond was lost on this train,"

220
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:22,680
"the reputation of Nakagawa Railway will be in a mess."

221
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:25,160
"No! Definitely not!"

222
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:29,640
"If you doubt it so much, then take a look!"

223
00:10:30,020 --> 00:10:32,300
"All right, Watson!"

224
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,000
"Me?"

225
00:10:34,820 --> 00:10:35,760
"You can find out."

226
00:10:38,060 --> 00:10:39,340
"Excuse me."

227
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:40,360
"Go ahead."

228
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:45,160
"But Ryo, I understand your motive, but that's not all."

229
00:10:45,740 --> 00:10:47,060
