233
00:10:53,140 --> 00:10:55,920
"Damn it! I can't beat him!"

234
00:10:57,060 --> 00:10:58,080
"You're right."

235
00:10:59,900 --> 00:11:01,860
"It's not anywhere, Ryo."

236
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:03,760
"What? That can't be!"

237
00:11:04,180 --> 00:11:05,720
"Did you find it, Elari?"

238
00:11:06,020 --> 00:11:06,620
